                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": "In order to examine the potential of appropriate software architecture, we will take into account three diverse use cases into our case studies in the agrofood sector, which takes into account most of the requirements and challenges across the domain. The three use cases chosen for the understanding and development of robotic architectures are harvesting robots, food processing robots, and food packaging. These use- case projects have some similar requirements in terms of functionality and performance as well as different requirements. In the subsequent sections, we are going to explore and exploit similarities in software and hardware architectures to be needed in all three use cases."
